## ğŸ”‘ API Endpoints

### ğŸ‘¤ Auth

- `POST /api/users/register` â†’ Register new user
- `POST /api/users/login` â†’ Login user

### ğŸ“¦ Products

- `GET /api/product` â†’ Get all products
- `GET /api/product/:id` â†’ Get single product
- `POST /api/product` â†’ Create product (Admin)
- `PUT /api/product/:id` â†’ Update product (Admin)
- `DELETE /api/product/:id` â†’ Delete product (Admin)

### ğŸ›’ Cart

- `GET /api/cart` â†’ Get user cart
- `POST /api/cart/:productId` â†’ Add item to cart
- `DELETE /api/cart/:productId` â†’ Remove item from cart
